asset.author: Shark Cleaning

transcripts: Amy duo clean technology blows away the myth that you need a larger heavier vacuum to have tremendous deep carpet cleaning power let me show you. Okay we poured craft beads, dirt, pet food, coffee beans, sand, cereal and coffee grounds on this carpet and made this crazy kind of mess you normally cringe to try to vacuum up but watch the Shark. Look at that duo clean technology, two brush rolls working in unison to deep clean this carpet. We've got a soft brush roll in front that pulls in the larger particles and then a second brush all working together with the first one look at that, this is incredible. The smaller particles that are deeply embedded inside the carpet that are being picked up at the same time as a larger particles. Two brush rolls is a completely breakthrough new kind of cleaning technology no one has ever done this before. Look at that. Nicely done.
